 <span data-ttu-id="581bd-144">Anwendungen können den Wert von <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A>vollständig ändern.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="581bd-144">Applications are free to completely change the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="581bd-145">Wenn Sie den Wert von <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A> zurücksetzen, wird der Wert <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextOffset%2A> von <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextLength%2A>und nicht geändert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="581bd-145">Resetting the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A> will not change the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextOffset%2A> and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextLength%2A>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
